{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e1436ee545","title":"给范长江的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6052d82ad3","index":0,"year":1937,"month":3,"day":29,"articleId":"e1436ee545"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c1678202bc","type":"paragraph","text":"给范长江的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"c39ccd1dd6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1937年3月29日）长江先生：谢意！那次很简慢你，对不住得很！你的文章”我们都看过了，深致寄上谈话叫一份，祭黄陵文一纸，籍供参考，可能时析为发布。甚盼时赐教言，医我不速敬颂摆祺！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"4566a331ff","type":"paragraph","text":"弟毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"622db6c719","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二十九日二十四时[1]范长江（1909-1970），四川内江人，新闻工作者。1937年2月等以大公报记者身份到西安和延安采访。1939年加入中国共产党，后长期在党的新闻部门做领导工作。[2]指范长江访问西安和延安后，在《大公报》上发表的报道西安事变真相和中国共产党抗日主张的新闻通讯。[3]指1937年3月1日毛泽东和美国作家史沫特莱的该话。这个谈话发表于1937年3月29日至4月3日延安《新中华报》.题为《中日问题与西安事变》4]指中华苏维埃共和国中央政府和人民抗日红军准备在1937年4月5日高。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"6f2812b5ad","type":"paragraph","text":"那次银所惯你，欢代银！你们文事我们新务医，除改谢是！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"9352286d4e","type":"paragraph","text":"实上读活一份，综员隆一很转位参考，能计新功发布世服时奶投言，区作一压台公次投发视！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"b74578dfd4","type":"paragraph","text":"子如气要","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"},{"id":"35f7d4d587","type":"paragraph","text":"三1u九nhan毛泽东致范长江信的手稿","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545"}],"page":{"id":"62ae85cc4a","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"e1436ee545","start":262,"end":263}}}},"__N_SSG":true}